        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "PSALM 97:1-2, 10-12\nADONAI malach tageil haaretz,\nyism'chu iyim rabim.\nAnan vaarafel s'vivav\ntzedek umishpat m'chon kiso.\nOhavei Adonai sinu ra,\nshomeir nafshot chasidav\nmiyad r’sha-im yatzileim.\nOr zarua latzaddik\nul'yishrei lev simchah.\nSimchu tzaddikim b'Adonai\nv'hodu l'zeicher kodsho.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
